your anger out on each other,

14:18.558 --> 14:21.028
try to find a little
common ground in your sorrow.

14:21.061 --> 14:23.530
- No, it's not the same thing.
I lost my wife.

14:23.563 --> 14:27.100
- Well, he lost his daughter.

14:27.134 --> 14:29.502
<i>[soft folk music]</i>

14:29.536 --> 14:31.905
- How about I start
taking your advice

14:31.939 --> 14:33.573
