20:13.212 --> 20:16.583
- Thank you, Tinsley.

20:17.550 --> 20:21.521
Hey, would you mind coming
by later to fix those wires,

20:21.554 --> 20:23.523
'cause I don't know
how to do that.

20:23.556 --> 20:26.359
I know you can hear me!

20:26.393 --> 20:27.694
[gasps] Jesus.

20:27.727 --> 20:29.462
- I was hopeful
that Singles Night

20:29.496 --> 20:31.030
